cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper introduces a new algorithm for semi-supervised learning using deep neural networks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm is applied to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks in the experiments. Additionally, the use of stochastic gradient descent and neural networks suggests a connection to neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
